titleInfo.title: Letter from William Newnham, Secretary to the Government at Bombay Castle, to Lieutenant William Bruce, Acting Resident at Bushire

mods.abstract: Letter from William Newnham, Secretary to the Government at Bombay Castle, to Lieutenant William Bruce, Acting Resident at Bushire, informing him that fifty-nine bales of unsold woollens received from Bushire were being returned.
